query:
SELECT j.id, j.assignedSupplierId, su.userId as supplierUserId, u.email as supplierEmail 
FROM jobs j 
LEFT JOIN supplierUsers su ON j.assignedSupplierId = su.supplierId 
LEFT JOIN users u ON su.userId = u.id 
WHERE j.id = 90001
